{
  "lesson": "WC-12-08",
  "audioMaster": "training/module12-settings/WC-12-08-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 384.026,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Two Settings areas face the customer directly, and this lesson reads both.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 4.455,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "In the left rail, open Customer Portal, then Portal Overview.",
      "startS": 4.907,
      "endS": 8.768,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "This hub is the portal your client's members log into, summarized on one screen:",
      "startS": 9.272,
      "endS": 13.935,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "its status, its address, and a version stamp.",
      "startS": 14.38,
      "endS": 17.638,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "It's live. Treat it that way.",
      "startS": 17.965,
      "endS": 19.726,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Read the tile band.",
      "startS": 20.16,
      "endS": 21.606,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "Registered members, logins today, average session, uptime, and the share on mobile.",
      "startS": 22.096,
      "endS": 23.192,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "When someone reports the portal is slow or quiet, this row is your first read.",
      "startS": 23.395,
      "endS": 24.49,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Healthy numbers here move the problem somewhere else.",
      "startS": 24.717,
      "endS": 36.131,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "Four cards sit below, one per configuration area.",
      "startS": 36.56,
      "endS": 39.667,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Branding, features, access, and content.",
      "startS": 40.015,
      "endS": 40.635,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Each card previews its own headline values,",
      "startS": 40.844,
      "endS": 41.422,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "like the login method and whether one time passwords are required.",
      "startS": 41.638,
      "endS": 43.072,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "You can answer most portal questions from these cards without opening anything.",
      "startS": 43.931,
      "endS": 53.92,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "Below the cards, two panels.",
      "startS": 54.32,
      "endS": 56.192,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Recent activity lists what members did in the last day, including a security line:",
      "startS": 56.574,
      "endS": 61.304,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "three failed login attempts from one address.",
      "startS": 61.642,
      "endS": 64.053,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Portal Health confirms the A-P-I connection, the certificate,",
      "startS": 64.506,
      "endS": 69.738,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "and when the portal was last published.",
      "startS": 69.995,
      "endS": 71.501,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "And note the button top right.",
      "startS": 71.752,
      "endS": 75.283,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Publish Changes pushes edits live to real customers. Support never clicks it.",
      "startS": 75.535,
      "endS": 77.158,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Open Branding and Appearance.",
      "startS": 77.6,
      "endS": 79.418,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Three tabs.",
      "startS": 79.939,
      "endS": 80.824,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Visual Identity holds the portal's name, tagline, logo, and header style,",
      "startS": 81.554,
      "endS": 88.04,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "with a live preview underneath.",
      "startS": 88.779,
      "endS": 92.171,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Everything a customer sees before signing in gets styled here.",
      "startS": 92.718,
      "endS": 94.759,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "There's a Save and Publish button at the bottom. We read; we never save.",
      "startS": 95.156,
      "endS": 96.96,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Next, Features and Modules.",
      "startS": 97.36,
      "endS": 99.477,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Every portal capability is a section here,",
      "startS": 100.169,
      "endS": 102.628,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "from membership plans to gift cards to vehicle management, each with its own sub options.",
      "startS": 102.832,
      "endS": 108.125,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "One catch: this page says nine of ten modules enabled, while the hub card said seven of nine.",
      "startS": 108.544,
      "endS": 114.409,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "The two disagree.",
      "startS": 114.795,
      "endS": 115.901,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "When you need the real number, read it here, and flag the mismatch.",
      "startS": 116.126,
      "endS": 119.92,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Open Access and Security, the page for login trouble.",
      "startS": 120.397,
      "endS": 123.651,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "The Authentication tab shows how members can sign in:",
      "startS": 124.5,
      "endS": 127.574,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "phone yes, email yes, membership number no, and no guest access.",
      "startS": 128.022,
      "endS": 133.034,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Below that, the one time password rules and the password policy.",
      "startS": 133.659,
      "endS": 137.488,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "A customer locked out of the portal? Start on this page, every time.",
      "startS": 137.8,
      "endS": 141.742,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "Then Content and Messaging.",
      "startS": 142.16,
      "endS": 144.021,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Welcome text, footer, contact details, and the FAQ list.",
      "startS": 144.559,
      "endS": 145.766,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Plain language a confused customer reads first.",
      "startS": 146.065,
      "endS": 146.447,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "If a member quotes the portal saying something odd, this is where that wording lives.",
      "startS": 146.736,
      "endS": 157.12,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "That's the portal.",
      "startS": 157.598,
      "endS": 158.663,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "For a login complaint, check two settings, the login method and whether O-T-P is required,",
      "startS": 159.319,
      "endS": 165.901,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "then look for failed attempts in the activity feed.",
      "startS": 166.285,
      "endS": 169.161,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "Back to Portal Overview, and remember the rule: nothing gets published, nothing gets saved.",
      "startS": 170.48,
      "endS": 176.242,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "Part two. In the left rail, open A-I Agent, then Overview.",
      "startS": 176.78,
      "endS": 177.477,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "This is the automated agent answering your client's customers on web chat, text, and phone.",
      "startS": 177.874,
      "endS": 181.906,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "The header says it's live on three channels.",
      "startS": 182.319,
      "endS": 187.732,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "Same posture as the portal: everything here is read only.",
      "startS": 188.202,
      "endS": 194.216,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "Read the metric band.",
      "startS": 194.64,
      "endS": 196.012,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "Conversations this month, average handle time, a satisfaction score.",
      "startS": 196.841,
      "endS": 198.301,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "The number to watch is containment rate,",
      "startS": 198.562,
      "endS": 201.172,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "the share of conversations the agent finished without a person.",
      "startS": 201.959,
      "endS": 209.291,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "Seventy eight percent here. When that slides, humans are picking up the slack.",
      "startS": 209.612,
      "endS": 212.374,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "Three channel cards.",
      "startS": 212.876,
      "endS": 214.099,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "Web chat carries the most volume and contains the most.",
      "startS": 214.934,
      "endS": 218.097,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "Text runs through a provisioned number with quiet hours on.",
      "startS": 218.632,
      "endS": 221.688,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "Voice is newer, still marked beta, with recording consent enabled.",
      "startS": 222.341,
      "endS": 224.481,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "Each card shows its own contained percentage, so you can spot which channel is struggling.",
      "startS": 224.781,
      "endS": 231.58,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "Now the capabilities panel.",
      "startS": 232.135,
      "endS": 233.461,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "Six actions the agent can take on its own,",
      "startS": 233.461,
      "endS": 237.082,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p63",
      "text": "from looking up an account to processing a small refund to escalating to a human.",
      "startS": 237.082,
      "endS": 242.587,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p64",
      "text": "They run through secure platform A-P-Is,",
      "startS": 242.587,
      "endS": 244.576,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p65",
      "text": "and each one can be switched off individually under Configuration.",
      "startS": 244.576,
      "endS": 247.891,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p66",
      "text": "Open Configuration.",
      "startS": 248.32,
      "endS": 249.09,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p67",
      "text": "Status tiles up top, including a refund cap of fifty dollars,",
      "startS": 249.09,
      "endS": 253.61,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p68",
      "text": "then five tabs covering identity, channels, tools, safety, and the model.",
      "startS": 253.61,
      "endS": 257.844,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p69",
      "text": "One caution: in the captured tenant this page renders as an unsaved form",
      "startS": 257.844,
      "endS": 263.295,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p70",
      "text": "for a different demo brand.",
      "startS": 263.295,
      "endS": 265.22,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p71",
      "text": "Read the structure, trust nothing as the live values, and never save.",
      "startS": 265.22,
      "endS": 270.193,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p72",
      "text": "Next, Knowledge Base.",
      "startS": 270.72,
      "endS": 271.781,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p73",
      "text": "These are the documents the agent searches before it answers,",
      "startS": 271.781,
      "endS": 275.84,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p74",
      "text": "so it quotes policy instead of guessing.",
      "startS": 275.84,
      "endS": 278.316,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p75",
      "text": "Tiles track articles, indexing, and the last sync.",
      "startS": 278.316,
      "endS": 281.991,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p76",
      "text": "In this capture the table sits empty, which is a tenant quirk, not the real agent.",
      "startS": 281.991,
      "endS": 288.51,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p77",
      "text": "Open Channels and Deployment, and keep your hands off the buttons.",
      "startS": 288.96,
      "endS": 290.647,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p78",
      "text": "Each channel block carries a test control:",
      "startS": 290.977,
      "endS": 293.156,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p79",
      "text": "send a test message, send a test text, place a test call.",
      "startS": 294.468,
      "endS": 296.683,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p80",
      "text": "All three reach a real channel.",
      "startS": 297.014,
      "endS": 298.286,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p81",
      "text": "None of them get clicked, ever, in the demo tenant.",
      "startS": 298.592,
      "endS": 299.861,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p82",
      "text": "Read the uptime and latency, and move on.",
      "startS": 300.204,
      "endS": 309.9,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p83",
      "text": "Then Conversations.",
      "startS": 310.389,
      "endS": 311.77,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p84",
      "text": "The transcript log: who talked to the agent, on which channel, about what, and how it ended.",
      "startS": 312.101,
      "endS": 313.074,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p85",
      "text": "This is your audit trail when a client asks what the agent actually said.",
      "startS": 313.464,
      "endS": 317.485,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p86",
      "text": "Empty in this capture, and the Export control stays untouched.",
      "startS": 317.949,
      "endS": 325.6,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s18",
      "id": "p87",
      "text": "Escalations is the page to remember.",
      "startS": 326.059,
      "endS": 327.975,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s18",
      "id": "p88",
      "text": "When the agent hits a limit, a refund over the cap, an angry customer,",
      "startS": 327.975,
      "endS": 333.078,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s18",
      "id": "p89",
      "text": "a direct ask for a manager, or a stalled conversation, it hands off here.",
      "startS": 333.078,
      "endS": 338.275,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s18",
      "id": "p90",
      "text": "Each row shows the reason, the priority, and who claimed it.",
      "startS": 338.275,
      "endS": 342.301,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s18",
      "id": "p91",
      "text": "Don't click Claim Next; that assigns a live escalation to you.",
      "startS": 342.301,
      "endS": 345.814,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s19",
      "id": "p92",
      "text": "Last, Analytics.",
      "startS": 346.24,
      "endS": 347.789,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s19",
      "id": "p93",
      "text": "The monthly review view: volume, containment, escalation rate, satisfaction,",
      "startS": 348.364,
      "endS": 353.757,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s19",
      "id": "p94",
      "text": "and what the agent costs to run, per channel and per conversation.",
      "startS": 354.08,
      "endS": 357.713,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s19",
      "id": "p95",
      "text": "When a client asks whether the agent is worth it, this page is the answer.",
      "startS": 358.537,
      "endS": 362.588,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s19",
      "id": "p96",
      "text": "Export stays alone here too.",
      "startS": 363.109,
      "endS": 364.794,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s20",
      "id": "p97",
      "text": "Two areas, one habit.",
      "startS": 365.262,
      "endS": 366.718,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s20",
      "id": "p98",
      "text": "The portal hub answers login complaints through the login method and O-T-P settings,",
      "startS": 366.718,
      "endS": 372.135,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s20",
      "id": "p99",
      "text": "and the agent hands humans a conversation through the Escalations queue,",
      "startS": 372.135,
      "endS": 376.138,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s20",
      "id": "p100",
      "text": "which mirrors into the C-R-M Agent Console.",
      "startS": 376.138,
      "endS": 378.971,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
